mg elements must have an alt prop, either with meaningful text, or an empty string for decorative images.","jsx-a11y/img-redundant-alt","Redundant alt attribute. Screen-readers already announce `img` tags as an image. You don’t need to use the words `image`, `photo,` or `picture` (or any specified custom words) in the alt prop.","no-script-url","Script URL is a form of eval.","Literal","unexpectedScriptURL","'ADDSTORYGENRE_SUCCESS' is defined but never used.","'ADDSTORYGENRE_FAIL' is defined but never used.","'ADD_STORY_GENRE_FAIL' is defined but never used.","'ADD_STORY_GENRE_SUCCESS' is defined but never used.","'UserService' is defined but never used.","import/no-anonymous-default-export","Unexpected default export of anonymous function","ExportDefaultDeclaration","Assign object to a variable before exporting as module default","'errorMessage' is assigned a value but never used.","'selectedGenre' is assigned a value but never used.","'content' is assigned a value but never used.","'loading' is assigned a value but never used.","'updatedList' is assigned a value but never used."]